es. Tous les exercices sont corrigés.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 25. Feb 2021) 0aMathematical analysis. 0aNumbers, Real. 4aMathematics. 7aMATHEMATICS / General.2bisacsh1 aNowak, Maria T, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759803200423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9782759803200.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MTPY  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK